Class TrigGraph

java.lang.Object
  |
  +--it.Graphable
        |
        +--it.TrigGraph
public class TrigGraph
extends Graphable

This class allows a simple trig function to be graphed over a given range. For complex trig functions the user should subclass Graphable and implement the necessary methods.

evaluateXY

protected final void evaluateXY(java.awt.geom.Point2D.Double p)
Evaluate f(x) for the trig graph. A valid x value is in the point p and a corresponding graph-space y value is calculated.
Parameters:
p - a double precision 2D point. On entry into this method p.x is valid and on exit p.y = f(x).
